headline: General Electric (GE): Exploring Valuation After Recent Momentum and Double-Digit Shareholder Returns
summary: General Electric (GE) shares edged slightly lower on Thursday, closing at $299.35. The move comes as investors weigh the company's recent performance. headline: Why Analysts See a Shifting Story for GE as Optimism and Risks Grow
summary: The consensus analyst price target for General Electric has recently inched up from $302.33 to $310.14, marking a modest upward revision. This increase reflects renewed optimism around GE Aerospace's performance and future growth prospects, as analysts highlight ongoing strength in the company's commercial engine business and continued robust order activity.
